release.name: chronicle-bom-2.24ea19
release.body:
### **chronicle-platform: 2.24ea5**
- [**closed**] FIX UI: Forbid editing the active session [#381](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/381)
- [**closed**] FIX UI: Enhance messageGenerator and messageNotifier type checks [#374](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/374)
- [**closed**] FIX UI: Fix FixGuiRouterCfg missing updates of FixSessionCfg [#371](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/371)
- [**closed**] Fix "jumping" selected options in "Select" components [#358](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/358)
- [**closed**] FIX GUI: when changing the routing rules, we have to click <submit> twice [#319](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/319)
- [**closed**] Show "Copy Search Query" button, even if search result is empty [#301](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/301)
- [**closed**] Fix FIX GUI crash, if there is no sessions pre-defined [#283](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/283)
- [**high-priority**] FIX UI: specify 'delegatingMessageParser' field in RouterMessageParser for Router sessions [#372](https://github.com/ChronicleEnterprise/Chronicle-Platform/issues/372)

### **chronicle-queue: 5.24ea6**
*No changelog for this release.*

### **jlbh: 1.23ea1**
*No changelog for this release.*
